summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 3210, for the improvement of the alley between 7th Avenue West and 8th Avenue West from West Highland Drive to West Blaine Street, all in the City of Seattle, under Ordinance No. 39665 and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
